    "body": "+1\n\nThis keeps the window in taskbar:\n\n``` javascript\nlet window = new BrowserWindow({\n      height: externalDisplay.size.height,\n      width: externalDisplay.size.width,\n      frame: false,\n      skipTaskbar: true\n    });\n```\n\nThis does not:\n\n``` javascript\nlet window = new BrowserWindow({\n      height: externalDisplay.size.height - 1,\n      width: externalDisplay.size.width,\n      frame: false,\n      skipTaskbar: true\n    });\n```\n\nWindows 10, Electron 1.2.8\n"
